README
------

* generate-basic-qrcode.py: demonstrates how to generate a basic QR code
  using the qrcode library

* generate-qrcode-with-image.py: demonstrates how to generate a QR code
  with image using both the qrcode module, and the Python Imaging Library 
  (PIL)

* python-logo.png: Python logo as PNG image file

* python-logo.png: Python logo as PNG image file
